    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frenemies 是一款可爱的多人游戏，最多 10 名玩家被困在荒岛上，接受生存和背叛的终极考验。 受热门电视节目《幸存者》启发，建立基地、结成联盟并战斗，成为这场社会欺骗游戏中最后存活下来的玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/4ae696dd375af545afae8a92a847eba7.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索岛屿并学习如何耕种、制作、烹饪、钓鱼等。 建立基地并完成任务，为你的新岛屿家园做出贡献。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/2704e9db7196291dc7c4096b85579908.poster.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/2704e9db7196291dc7c4096b85579908.webm?t=1757219577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/2704e9db7196291dc7c4096b85579908.mp4?t=1757219577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/f3d39381190618528539140278201725.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多个不同的岛屿上进行免疫之战，游戏模式包括捉鸡、海盗大战、雪球混乱、红灯绿灯、道具狩猎等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/e5bbadef2d34908ca0089ea5d79a16ae.poster.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/e5bbadef2d34908ca0089ea5d79a16ae.webm?t=1757219577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/e5bbadef2d34908ca0089ea5d79a16ae.mp4?t=1757219577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/a445e0728a96ebb4d4ce301596831a92.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投票消灭你的敌人，成为最后存活的玩家。 使用游戏内近距离聊天来建立联盟或背叛你的朋友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过激活强大的符文来影响投票来击败他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/27b684a9763cbc6a1b85f34a847979f8.poster.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/27b684a9763cbc6a1b85f34a847979f8.webm?t=1757219577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/27b684a9763cbc6a1b85f34a847979f8.mp4?t=1757219577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/4699eb7337d854d47284c458e20d600f.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为恶棍并在战斗中战斗并激活来自坟墓之外的暗影符文。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/462fa7135119200abd06bb3951c3ab51.poster.avif?t=1757219577\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/462fa7135119200abd06bb3951c3ab51.webm?t=1757219577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/c47bc781e6d3d903a133a1b9bb5b760f.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用多个玩家皮肤自定义您的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/512d97d09140711f987fd8b16ce3f737.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=420 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有可爱的宠物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387270/extras/fd4dd6c7a87b1b68ac1b423ba4a3875f.avif?t=1757219577\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p>",
